{"tid":1657502,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"按證公司：壓測不達標 首置人士仍可敘造9成按揭","createTime":"2019-10-16T06:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T10:49:41.000Z","uid":60281,"like":25,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"e50e8d210d0ac89f2046b7c0bc3952b43fa8f7ee","tid":1657502,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:24:04.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20191016/s00010/3ecad651b83d6be150717b2518a09f0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20191016%2Fs00010%2F3ecad651b83d6be150717b2518a09f0b.jpg&h=72eaa4ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1571204433651&amp;issue=20191016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1571204433651%26issue%3D20191016&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=341d3250\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1571204433651%26issue%3D20191016&h=76f2b0f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1571204433651&amp;issue=20191016</a><br />\n<br />\n施政報告公布放寬按保計劃的樓價上限後，按揭證券公司旗下按證保險公司宣布詳情，當中首次置業人士如未能符合壓力測試，仍可申請敘造最高8成或9成按揭貸款。<br />\n<br />\n修訂主要是將首次置業人士的9成按揭保險合資格物業價格上限，調高至800萬元；8成按揭保險的合資格物業價格上限調高至1000萬元。欲以高於修訂前的物業價格上限（即8成按揭保險下的600萬元及9成按揭保險下的400萬元）敍造按揭貸款，須繳交額外15%的保險費用，保費可隨每月按揭還款攤分，上述和現有按揭保險產品的供款入息比率統一以50%為上限，並須符合銀行壓力測試。<br />\n<br />\n不過，按證保險公司指出，首次置業人士如未能符合壓力測試，仍可申請敘造最高8成或9成按揭貸款，其保費會因應風險因素作額外調整。<br />\n<br />\n上述修訂即日生效。"},{"pid":"66a7117c8487f63cecc5d7c3781c2dba60fa9539","tid":1657502,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHn4YGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHn4YGm.jpg&h=a9bf801a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1f49bd216232187bdebb57d1855757e1d9e1ae3a","tid":1657502,"uid":242537,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:25:04.000Z","msg":"多多都借俾佢,等佢死得大鑊啲! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8757eda8a8067ee6865853404b7644f7256ecf4b","tid":1657502,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:25:55.000Z","msg":"轉按計唔計？"},{"pid":"f03fa7408a61127e5b42c274d909199217b96b2c","tid":1657502,"uid":74155,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:27:16.000Z","msg":"㧬人落個死氹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca083f891d900f37bbb5b2b4f8a3b44282f77a9a","tid":1657502,"uid":62270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:28:17.000Z","msg":"想人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n17/10(Thu)： 12點調景嶺HKDI集會<br />\n18/10(Fri)： 5點港大反警暴集會，7點18區面具人鏈<br />\n19/10(Sat)： 7點半遮打國際人道救援祈禱會<br />\n20/10(Sun)： 1點半九龍民陣大遊行<br />\n21/10(Mon)： 7點元朗靜坐<br />\n25/10(Fri)： 朝早7點九龍港島和你返工"},{"pid":"100dcf10fb214c57dfd53324ad9a57d59568dfd2","tid":1657502,"uid":61882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1f49bd216232187bdebb57d1855757e1d9e1ae3a","tid":1657502,"uid":242537,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:25:04.000Z","msg":"多多都借俾佢,等佢死得大鑊啲! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:28:19.000Z","msg":"喂！你學過