月按揭還款攤分，上述和現有按揭保險產品的供款入息比率統一以50%為上限，並須符合銀行壓力測試。<br />\n<br />\n不過，按證保險公司指出，首次置業人士如未能符合壓力測試，仍可申請敘造最高8成或9成按揭貸款，其保費會因應風險因素作額外調整。<br />\n<br />\n上述修訂即日生效。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"因為樓市頂唔順，只有用依個方法去支撐樓市令佢不跌反升，不要中計"},{"pid":"1c0fa7f5a4eec6a12795aacb7ae4a1cbc71708c5","tid":1657502,"uid":124473,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6dbb2a71982ef1088e48b48cce11c6853400ac49","tid":1657502,"uid":32842,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"34905ded7be04016ca818f766128363c873c50bc","tid":1657502,"uid":255150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d517bb7b3b704dd334303b5492aef71fbf7eddf2","tid":1657502,"uid":124473,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:41:49.000Z","msg":"兩公婆夾埋搵8萬<br />\n供3萬都ok既..."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:42:25.000Z","msg":"香港入息中位數 你知唔知係幾錢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:47:09.000Z","msg":"夾埋搵8萬唔洗9成按啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:49:50.000Z","msg":"可能你仲後生<br />\n大把人30中尾搵4,5萬<br />\n又拎唔到個首期出黎..."},{"pid":"bc7101c9a144b731c239e911d267794ac1a1db87","tid":1657502,"uid":274722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:50:35.000Z","msg":"痴線，波叔先係咁警告經濟會急速轉差失業率上升，林奠就谷人上車㩜炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1923f1f81a31a6b021017f5f7e5b92458fbf68d5","tid":1657502,"uid":124473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34905ded7be04016ca818f766128363c873c50bc","tid":1657502,"uid":255150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d517bb7b3b704dd334303b5492aef71fbf7eddf2","tid":1657502,"uid":124473,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b555f28a2a22bcc4748ce5e54506b8497e324c84","tid":1657502,"uid":255150,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:38